Attachments Building Block

Allow to download categorized attachments on website

Main Features:

  • Groups of Attachments
  • Drop Attachment Groups on Pages
  • Public & Private Attachments

Groups of Attachments

This module allows you to create groups of attachments and add them to the website for visitors to download.

This helps a lot when you need to provide some specifications or manuals for the products you sell.

Drop Attachment Groups on Pages

Drag & Drop attachments building block on any page you want on your website. Select from pre-created attachment groups.

Public & Private Attachments

Attachments can be public which will allow all users and visitors to download them. Also attachments can be private which means that only logged-in users will be able to download them.
